mysql> describe transaction;
+------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field            | Type          | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| transaction_id   | int(10)       | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| transaction_type | varchar(14)   | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| transaction_amt  | decimal(10,2) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| date             | date          | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| sales_channel    | varchar(14)   | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| payment_method   | varchar(10)   | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| Customer_id      | int(10)       | NO   | MUL | NULL    |                |
| Agent_id         | int(10)       | NO   | MUL | NULL    |                |
+------------------+---------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
8 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> describe agent;
+-------------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field       | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+-------------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| agent_id    | int(10)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| name        | varchar(20) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| address     | varchar(50) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| agent_type  | varchar(14) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| date        | date        | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| location_id | int(10)     | NO   | MUL | NULL    |                |
| pincode     | int(10)     | NO   |     | NULL    |                |

    -> from policy_fact INNER JOIN agent ON policy_fact.agent_dim_id=agent_dim.agent_dim_id INNER JOIN location_dim ON agent_dim.location_id = location_dim.location_id
    ->  INNER JOIN calender_dim ON policy_fact.date_key=calender_dim.date_key
    -> group by agent.agent_id having EXTRACT(year FROM calender_dim.date) = 2012 and policy_fact.transaction_type = "CANCEL";

    -> INNER JOIN calender_dim on calender_dim.date_key = policy_fact.date_key
    -> INNER JOIN agent_dim on agent_dim.agent_dim_id = policy_fact.agent_dim_id
    -> INNER JOIN location_dim on location_dim.location_id = agent_dim.location_id
    -> where calender_dim.year = '2012' and policy_fact.transaction_type = 'CANCEL'
